<span id="freeTextContainer5371142059672554753">This is a new revised version of Dr. Laslett&apos;s standard edition of Two Treatises. First published in 1960, and based on an analysis of the whole body of Locke&apos;s publications, writings, and papers. The Introduction and text have been revised to incorporate references to recent scholarship since the second edition and the bibliography has been updated.</span>
