<div id="review_3397703439" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3397703439" />
    <a title="Alvaro Mallo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/101317889-alvaro-mallo"><img alt="Alvaro Mallo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1576337477p2/101317889.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3397703439?book_show_action=true">Jun 17, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alvaro Mallo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alvaro Mallo" href="/user/show/101317889-alvaro-mallo">Alvaro Mallo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3397703439" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6633868619817009720">I had to read this for college. But I have read it anyway. Locke establish the pillars of liberalism. But I found his work lesser than that of Hobbes. </span>

          </span>
